edu.cpp.cs.cs141.vetadmin

Class Pet

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.vetadmin.Pet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Pet>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cat, Dog, Fish

    public abstract class Pet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Pet>, java.io.Serializable
    This abstract class represents a pet. It contains the pet's Owner, name, AnimalType, age, medical history (medHist), vaccinations, and appointments.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
